<paragraph blockId="14.[178,1085,1418,1498]" pageId="14" pageNumber="943">
R e m a r k s: there are insufficient data to make any valid conclusions about the status of this species in 
<collectingCountry box="[357,433,1447,1469]" name="Turkey" pageId="14" pageNumber="943">Turkey</collectingCountry>
. The bionomics is still unknown but is probably very similar to this of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="LEDERER" baseAuthorityYear="1853" box="[248,439,1477,1498]" class="Insecta" family="Sesiidae" genus="Pyropteron" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="943" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mannii">
<emphasis box="[248,439,1477,1498]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="943">Pyropteron mannii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The suspected food plant is a 
<emphasis box="[753,855,1476,1498]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="943">Geranium</emphasis>
species.
</paragraph>
